= What is Twisted? =

[wiki:TwistedProject Twisted] is an event-driven networking engine written in Python and licensed under the [http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php MIT license].  

See [wiki:FrequentlyAskedQuestions the FAQ] for commonly asked questions about Twisted.

